===Amaḍal n waɛraben akk d yenselmen===
[[Tugna:Image-Al-Kitāb_al-muḫtaṣar_fī_ḥisāb_al-ğabr_wa-l-muqābala.jpg|thumb|120px|Asebter n ''Aljiber'' n [[Abu Ǧaɛfar Muḥemmed Ibn Musa al-Xuwarzmi|Xuwarzmi]]]]


'''Aljiber''' yekk'd deg [[taɛrabt]] al-ǧabr, yuqal ''algebra'' s [[Talatinit|telatinit]], anamek is yezzi ugar ɣer '''Asdakkel'''(la reunion) n iceqqfan, neɣ '''tuqqna''' (la connexion). Akken daɣen ig wwi inumak(sens) nniḍen deg [[Tutlayt|tutlayin]] nniḍen.

D'awal ig llan ger wawalen imezwura i sqedcen s tutlayt taɛrabt,  adlis id yessufeɣ [[Abu Ǧaɛfar Muḥemmed Ibn Musa al-Xuwarzmi|Xuwarzmi]] isemma-y-as [[al-ǧabr wa el mouqabalah]], izrew dges aṭṭas n [[Tanzeggit|tenzeggit]] , i wumi ass agi leqdic ines nessemlal it ugar ɣer [[Tanzeggit taljibrit|tenzeggit taljibrit]].

Yiwet tikkelt [[Leonardo Fibonacci|Leonard de Pise]] i win mi qqaren [[Leonardo Fibonacci|Fibonacci]] yerza ɣer [[Tafriqt ugafa| tefriqt n ugafa]], ira(aimer) amek ttarun [[Azwil|izwilen]] deg tama agi n wemaḍal, deg imir yesseqdac izwilen akini, yerna yewwiten id ɣer [[Turuft]].

